rows.label: qst201909_0010
rows.name:
We finally found you, you
black-feathered fools.

rows.label: qst201909_0020
rows.name: ...Who are you, mo?

rows.label: qst201909_0030
rows.name:
Not content with deceiving our pure selves,
you now make a lovely girl cry, you deviants.

rows.label: qst201909_0040
rows.name: Your wicked meddling ends here and now!

rows.label: qst201909_0050
rows.name:
Who's that woman, mo? What's
she so worked up about, mo?

rows.label: qst201909_0060
rows.name: ...Ah, that woman. I remember her, mo.

rows.label: qst201909_0070
rows.name:
The clueless one who paid one million
gold for an empty island, mo.

rows.label: qst201909_0080
rows.name: Ahahahaha! Is that a joke, mo?

rows.label: qst201909_0090
rows.name: What a fool, mo!

rows.label: qst201909_0100
rows.name: ...Fufu.

rows.label: qst201909_0110
rows.name:
To mock us, how ignorant
of your own place.

rows.label: qst201909_0120
rows.name: Are you prepared for the consequences?

rows.label: qst201909_0130
rows.name:
Huh? We don't need
anything like that, mo.

rows.label: qst201909_0140
rows.name: What can you do, mo?

rows.label: qst201909_0150
rows.name: Divine punishment!

rows.label: qst201909_0160
rows.name:
Now, whoever wishes to become
a star next, step forward.

rows.label: qst201909_0170
rows.name: W-Wait, mo! Calm down, mo!

rows.label: qst201909_0180
rows.name:
W-We have our reasons,
mo! Let us explain, mo!

rows.label: qst201909_0190
rows.name:
We will not listen to
the words of you fools.

rows.label: qst201909_0200
rows.name: Prepare yourselves.

rows.label: qst201909_0210
rows.name: Hey, wait a minute, Rinne.

rows.label: qst201909_0220
rows.name:
Do not interfere, Rex. Do you
wish to be kicked away as well?

rows.label: qst201909_0230
rows.name:
If you kick them, you won't
get your money back.

rows.label: qst201909_0240
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]!

rows.label: qst201909_0250
rows.name: I see... That is indeed true.

rows.label: qst201909_0260
rows.name:
We should listen to what
they have to say first.

rows.label: qst201909_0270
rows.name:
We can always bring down the
hammer of justice later, right?

rows.label: qst201909_0280
rows.name:
Well... if Nia says so, we
suppose we could listen.

rows.label: qst201909_0290
rows.name: ...Alright. State your circumstances.

rows.label: qst201909_0300
rows.name: However...

rows.label: qst201909_0310
rows.name:
...you know what will happen if you
try to deceive us, do you not?

rows.label: qst201909_0320
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Hiiiieee!
